Description: ======
        TOPAZ
        ======
        
        TOPAZ (TOol for Plotting Aurora's Metals) is a Python package 
        
        Installation
        ------------
        TOPAZ can be installed with pip:
        
        ``pip install topaz``
        
        The developement version is avaliable by cloning this repository:
        
        ::
        
          git clone https://github.com/abatten/topaz
          cd topaz
          pip install -e .
        
